{"tid":408980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有無二次神作超越到「佢家下黃色衫，又變返綠色衫」","createTime":"2017-09-21T16:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T16:51:15.000Z","uid":143026,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c92fdb72c4b1526122d07159452e8b3b52245c","tid":408980,"uid":143026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"當年日日要睇個MV一次先瞓得着，雖然哩幾年都有好多高汁二次創作歌，但真心好笑哩套真係無得輸（淨就歡樂而言，唔計當中含義嘲諷咁計），重點係歌詞對到MV又無違和感。<br />\n<br />\n連登有無大神可以創作到歌詞配合到MV嘅二次創作歌出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「佢家下黃色衫，又變返綠色衫」<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RKaGuRaR3eo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKaGuRaR3eo&d=UUejqy2kXBjhLKw8KQR0INtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=06514823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RKaGuRaR3eo</a><br />\n<br />\n個人最鍾意個句&ldquo;我估佢條底褲 攬錯左上頭頂lu&rdquo;，再望一望佢頭頂塊白布，真心笑左<br />\n<br />\n不厭其煩再講一次 支持二次創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d6f1467ebd201e2a87ba77ab362a1393f10c6b","tid":408980,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔講你知,咋唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}